    DocletEnvironment
    public class MDocletEnvironment
extends jdk.javadoc.internal.tool.DocEnvImpl
implements DocletEnvironment
    Wraps the DocEnvImpl passed to the doclet for the sole purpose of inserting a wrapper for the doctrees access.
